law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 78, sec. 36, effective January 1, 1973. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 222, sec. 7, effective June 17, 1954. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4961.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Employee who rejects provisions of chapter is subject to common-law defenses.
